reviewText: The Holy Spirit is moving in exceedingly wonderful and new ways: Unity and Realization of *One God* amongst all the diverse Faiths *across the world*, a wonderful presentation of the Catholic Pope's Jewish Concertmaster and Abrahamic Muslim, Christian and Jewish faiths Honoring The Creator!!! Great PBS full length beautiful presentation with additional behind the scenes, interview that didn't make it into the PBS show.
Loved the music and enjoyed the documentary of some of the cities mentioned in the DVD as they related to the music.
